#EndSARS campaigner and popular comedian, Debo Adedayo, Mr Macaroni, has said he does not hate against any government official. Although he didn’t mention any name, Mr Macaroni stated that he is just interested in ensuring every Nigerian attains better life. He said: “I was at an event day before yesterday, a top government worker walks up to me and asks why I hate “someone” ~ I can’t mention name.   Nigerians to pay more for chicken, fish     PDP, APC in war of words over Ebubeagu     Senator seeks end to killing of Nigerians in South Africa   “I have no hate whatsoever in my heart. - Advertisement - “I just want a better life for every Nigerian. “I don’t hate anyone. We all can do better.”